<item>
            <title>[LU-19049] Build fix for new python/swig on Debian 13 (trixie)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19049</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Update the config/ac_python_devel.m4 to handle distutils being removed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Handle swig 4.3 api change, SWIG_Python_AppendOutput() takes a 3rd argument &apos;is_null&apos;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;SWIG_Python_AppendOutput(PyObject* result, PyObject* obj, int is_void) {
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Check version and pass 0 if needed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;+#if SWIG_VERSION &amp;gt;= 0x040300     
+    $result = SWIG_Python_AppendOutput($result,obj,0);
+#else
     $result = SWIG_Python_AppendOutput($result,obj);
+#endif
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
